#### TypeScript SDK Code Sample

```typescript
import { createClient } from 'liferay-headless-rest-client';
import { getExportTaskContent } from 'liferay-headless-rest-client/headless-batch-engine-v1.0';

const client = createClient({
    baseUrl: 'http://localhost:8080',
    headers: {
        Authorization: `Basic ${btoa("test@liferay.com:test")}`,
    },
});

async function main() {
    const { data } = await getExportTaskContent({
        client,
        path: {
           exportTaskId: "4979",
        },
    });

    console.log(data);
}
```
#### Java installation:

A Java client JAR is available for use with the group ID 'com.liferay', artifact ID 'com.liferay.headless.batch.engine.client', and version '1.0.28'.

```gradle
implementation group: "com.liferay", name: "com.liferay.headless.batch.engine.client", version: "latest"
```

Reference: https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/com.liferay/com.liferay.headless.batch.engine.client/latest

